      • setTimeout

        io.netty.util.concurrent.Future<Long> setTimeout(long timeoutMs)
        return previous timeout value. Possible null if the client is already closed.

        boolean isOpen()
        return whether the client is still open.

      • release

        void release()
        return the client to its pool if:
        1. The client is created by a NedisClientPool.
        2. The pool is exclusive.
